data.description: Absolutely stunning 3BR/3.5BA home nestled on 3.04 level acres, boasting YEAR ROUND BREATHTAKING MOUNTAIN VIEWS! This home has been REMODELED and is a true gem, featuring a spacious open living room and kitchen area with stainless steel appliances and a walk in pantry! Large Master bedroom/bath on the main level with double vanities, jacuzzi tub and a walk in tiled shower. Laundry room on the main level. The full-finished basement includes a great room, bonus guest room/bathroom, game room, secure safe room and ample storage space, ensuring both safety and functionality. With a two-car garage and a large workshop/storage building and a two-car detached carport. This property offers plenty of room for your vehicles, hobbies, and storage needs with Fiber Optic Internet. Fenced yard and so much more! This is a must-see property that combines beauty, space, and functionality in one exceptional package! Best of all it is less than 5 miles to downtown Blairsville! Call me today!
